      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those seeking a major project or a parts donor. The engine requires significant repair to be roadworthy, and the exterior shows heavy wear, including noticeable rust, large dents, and fading paint. The interior also requires a complete overhaul due to torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. Please come prepared with a trailer as it is not currently drivable.",
